# ── AI assistant instructions ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CLAUDE.md contains operating instructions for AI assistants and must not be
# committed — it may reference internal conventions, tooling details, or project
# context that should not be public.
CLAUDE.md

# ── Go build artefacts ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Test binary, built with `go test -c`
*.test

# Code coverage profiles and other test artifacts
*.out
coverage.*
*.coverprofile
profile.cov

# Dependency directories (remove the comment below to include it)
# vendor/

# Go workspace file
go.work
go.work.sum

# ── TLS certificates and private keys ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated locally; never commit private key material.
*.pem
*.key
*.crt

# ── Environment / secrets ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*

# ── Terraform ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# State files contain plaintext resource attributes including the service
# account private key generated in terraform/iam.tf — never commit them.
terraform/terraform.tfstate
terraform/terraform.tfstate.backup
terraform/.terraform/
terraform/.terraform.lock.hcl
terraform/*.tfplan

# ── Editor / IDE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
